# WideMCP — Cursor Agent Rules
# Read this file every session. No exceptions.

---

## 1. What is WideMCP

WideMCP is a curated catalogue of production-quality, open source MCP
(Model Context Protocol) servers with an orchestration layer on top.

Platform identity: Local-first. Privacy-first. Production-grade.
Domain: widemcp.dev
GitHub: github.com/widemcp
npm scope: @widemcp

Every tool in the catalogue is:
- Open source and free
- Runs on the user's machine — nothing sent to WideMCP servers
- Auto-installs dependencies with user permission
- Scored with an automated Trust Score before publishing

---

