Active phase: Phase 0 — Foundation
Active sprint: Sprint 0.2 — Hello World MCP Server
Current goal: A working TypeScript MCP server with one echo tool
responding inside Claude Desktop.

UPDATE THIS SECTION AT THE START OF EVERY NEW SPRINT.

