## 15. Commit Message Format

type(scope): short description

Types: feat, fix, docs, test, refactor, chore
Scope: av-server, ha-server, shared, orchestrator, desktop-app, docs

Examples:
feat(av-server): add yt-dlp download_audio tool
test(av-server): add integration tests for ffmpeg convert_media
fix(shared): handle missing dependency gracefully
docs(av-server): update README with sox examples

